{
  "stem": "25381.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was just standing to wipe out-- the blood was still on the second day, was still dried off from the day that they killed her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he didn't get me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The bullet went into the wall, and I was alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he was kind of upset.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That means, next time he'll-- he'll do it a better job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Like he didn't pull the-- you know, did straight to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they took a lot of advantages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Finally, it came one day and they gave us notice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that's the way it went like a whole year, while we were still in the homes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We had to go in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They took like two-- two streets, and they made with barricades with the wires, like a fence, real tall fence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It's like in a jail, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then-- in what in the jail for them was better.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Like the day in jail, it's a lot if-- because they have-- I see on television.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I've never been in jail, but I see on television-- they have a lot of land, and they walk around outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They doing exercise and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took like two big blocks and they barricade it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the men separate, the woman separate, and the young girls separate, the middle age separate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they pulled the ladies and we used to sleep in like a room like 25, 30 girls.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We slept on the floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just had straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were you with your mother and your sisters at this time?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we went to the ghetto, so we went all together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're not allowed to take anything except whatever you can put on on you, like another-- I took another slip, and another slip, and another dress.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How much can you carry?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
